ent-RMCPatchSPPNaval-name = SPP Naval Infantry patch
ent-RMCPatchSPPNaval-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the SPP Naval Infantry.

ent-RMCPatchSPPVDV-name = SPP Airborne Reconnaissance patch
ent-RMCPatchSPPVDV-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the 173rd Airborne Reconnaissance Platoon.

ent-RMCPatchSPP-name = SPP patch
ent-RMCPatchSPP-desc = An old fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the Socialists Progressive Peoples Armed Vanguard.

ent-RMCPatchWeYaFury161-name = Weston-Yamada Fury '161' patch
ent-RMCPatchWeYaFury161-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch. Was worn by workers and then later prisoners on the Fiorina 'Fury' 161 facility, a rare relic, after the facility went dark in 2079.

ent-RMCPatchWeYa-name = Weston-Yamada patch
ent-RMCPatchWeYa-desc = A fire-resistant white shoulder patch featuring the Weston-Yamada logo. A symbol of loyalty to the corporation, or perhaps ironic mockery, depending on your viewpoint.

ent-RMCPatchSolarDevils-name = UNMC Solar Devils patch
ent-RMCPatchSolarDevils-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the 3rd Battalion 'Solar Devils', part of the UNMC 2nd Division, 1st Regiment.

ent-RMCPatchFORECON-name = UNMC Force Reconnaissance patch
ent-RMCPatchFORECON-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the UNS Hanyut, UNMC FORECON.

ent-RMCPatchSEA-name = UNMC Senior Enlisted Advisor patch
ent-RMCPatchSEA-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the Falling Falcons, the 2nd battalion of the 4th brigade of the UNMC. The bottom reads "THIS WE'LL DEFEND" in silver embroidery.

ent-RMCPatchFallingFalcons-name = UNMC Falling Falcons patch
ent-RMCPatchFallingFalcons-desc = A fire-resistant shoulder patch, worn by the men and women of the Falling Falcons, the 2nd battalion of the 4th brigade of the UNMC.

